question: What is the name of the administrative center of Cēsu novads (Cēsis county) in Latvia?
asked_question_translated: Care este numele centrului administrativ al Cēsu novads (județul Cēsis) din Letonia?
answer: Centrul administrativ al județului Cēsis (Cēsu novads) din Letonia este orașul Cēsis.
answer_translated_eng: The administrative centre of Cēsis County (Cēsu novads) in Latvia is the city of Cēsis.
